{"tid":1631482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢撚的少少建議","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:37:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T15:51:45.000Z","uid":66577,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"dbca5deefc26c8ef127e98899d02f3c18305516d","tid":1631482,"uid":66577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:37:46.000Z","msg":"香港人要進步，唔該下次出黎唔好再尻流流<br />\n我有少少建議俾大家，希望大家聽得入耳同埋會進步<br />\n<br />\n1.認清自己定位<br />\n勇武=魔師/戰士<br />\n前線=哨兵/first aid/建築師/搬運兵<br />\n支援=傘兵(拎遮擋記者同埋花生友)/物資兵(唔該有能力就帶兩枝水、可以就幫手袋隻3m手套)<br />\n和理非=叫口號(可以的話唔該印定文宣出黎邊行邊貼)<br />\n垃圾=行到前一前又唔知做乜,情侶出黎散步拍拖,傻尻式自拍影相po ig<br />\n支援同埋和理非冇gear，如果見紅旗就慢慢企散向後，方便黑旗時大家退,唔會俾人圍捕<br />\n係到提下前線同勇武，我希望大家可以進步下，做一件事前要先思考<br />\n最簡單就係聽到有狗之後要定軍心，搞清狗既位置，思考後退路線同埋roadblock點放<br />\n另外唔該唔好俾憤怒控制自己，記住你地係為乜企出黎<br />\n<br />\n2.明白活動意義<br />\n宗旨：反抗極權,爭取雙普選,維護港人權益,重建未來<br />\n運作：不被捕&gt;黑裝修/紅裝飾(美心集團、吉野家例外,裝埋修)/銀行裝飾&gt;叫口號&gt;撚狗<br />\n不被捕=永續活動<br />\n裝修/裝飾=打壓紅色資本,增加運作費用<br />\n叫口號=話俾政權同埋國際知,香港人仲有膽出黎企出黎打過,同時國際文宣<br />\n撚狗=激完班狗之後食tear gas<br />\n<br />\n3.永遠唔打陣地<br />\n記住勇武同前線既比例係場活動其實好少架咋，唔好以為出黎幾萬人就可以同狗硬打<br />\n人地有裝有槍，仲有埋水炮車同狗車運輸，呢種情況仲衝埋去叫送頭，唔係叫打狗<br />\n記住輕裝既我地要打就打遊擊，邊走邊對付我地既敵人<br />\n你記住我地輕裝可以快,可以十八區開花,但係我地真係冇能力同狗仔係大馬路到正面硬碰<br />\n<br />\n4.退之有理<br />\n大家向後跑時唔好再驚慌咁走,唔該叫下發生左乜事<br />\n例如:「前面銅鑼灣二期廿隻防暴,前線叫退,一齊向後走」,而唔係一味尻跑<br />\n如果緊急又冇咁好氣咪:「前面有狗,前線叫走,一齊退」<br />\n簡單、清晰、易明就好,唔好搞到自己跑完都唔知乜事<br />\n另外我好希望旗手可以重新出現番,幫手統籌大局<br />\n最後提提大家,我地退場唔係完場<br />\n走唔係逃兵,係為左之後再出黎對付呢個極權<br />\n<br />\n5.勇武同前線要清楚地理位置<br />\n特別係哨,你地需要知道發生緊乜事,如果連乜街打乜街都唔清<br />\n你地點指揮大局?雖然係冇大台,但一場幾萬人既活動一定要有人清楚自己做緊乜<br />\n去政總拋石,去對黑社會用火魔法?一或俾和理非去做場萬人show(冇可能架喇,咪撚再FF)?<br />\n你地要清楚自己搞緊乜,同時最重要係要知道,狗佈左防未,佈邊到,而家要點走<br />\n因此我地需要好好了解位置同地理,我建議如果出去前大家可以print定地圖帶出去睇,真心有用<br />\n<br />\n6.對準政權與敵人<br />\n係到提提大家，唔該鍵戰幫手搵搵福建幫相關既大本營、建制狗既office同埋工聯會幫垃圾<br />\n你地唔係唔記得我地仇人係乜人呀?"},{"pid":"18b94012472d66be0afad3bde3f2706fd4e0c7cf","tid":1631482,"uid":126217,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:40:07.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"be47ffeb25457e23db238b0999a01bac37eccc42","tid":1631482,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「極重要」《三份英國外交及國會報告》：當代及後世香港抗爭者之啟示</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631132\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631132</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"85b553835d1d5018279438bbf234f4ecaa63c5fb","tid":1631482,"uid":66577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:44:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76018a34715ed0be72a26e98e0563081af0e5119","tid":1631482,"uid":164747,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:46:12.000Z","msg":"呢家愈黎愈多人見到狗就跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前都唔會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個月成日行行下前面啲人都返轉頭行/跑，但轉個頭個又可以繼續向前行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"494743d50bb6882cb5b0184921b57dc662f28f9a","tid":1631482,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:47:27.000Z","msg":"呢d POST就無人推"},{"pid":"b88c73774a5bc128b2eeb869944c1a25514346b6","tid":1631482,"uid":246422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"76018a34715ed0be72a26e98e0563081af0e5119","tid":1631482,"uid":164747,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:46:12.000Z","msg":"呢家愈黎愈多人見到狗就跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前都唔會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個月成日行行下前面啲人都返轉頭行/跑，但轉個頭個又可以繼續向前行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:47:51.000Z","msg":"成日調頭跑 但前面乜都冇。。。"},{"pid":"044914f0185429086a1bc30928a4f056c4977655","tid":1631482,"uid":66577,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:48:02.000Z","msg":"仲有前線個班兄弟<br />\n唔好再失控喇 對準政權"},{"pid":"f874562f53489fb4b5233a361b0ef351ca61955c","tid":1631482,"uid":66577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:50:34.000Z","msg":"推 用下腦睇下嘢"},{"pid":"806025d9dd79c343b8178bb78d802174fe45b2dc","tid":1631482,"uid":246422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:50:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14ab2b7daa59885852ba3c5f3956c6957a96024f","tid":1631482,"uid":66577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:51:02.000Z","msg":"唔好再失控喇大家<br />\n唔好再陣地喇<br />\n我真係好攰呀"},{"pid":"0c8fb15472e8c29587465d7817e221860f5343f2","tid":1631482,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:52:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果星期一晚18區開花失敗  就代表大家默許左呢條惡法</span><br />\n因為第日市面會如常運作<br />\n大家星期五講到有幾嬲有幾難接受 原來到上班日馬照跑舞照跳既?<br />\ncarrie仲有咩好驚呀?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">10月7號 18區啊 夜晚8點呀</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/33EUVX5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F33EUVX5.jpg&h=293eada8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">18區呀<br />\n18區呀</span></span><br />\n罷工文宣啊<br />\n行動Post呀<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求下大家打返一場靚既三罷 起碼要8.5既級數先</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果星期一晚18區開花失敗  就代表大家默許左呢條惡法"},{"pid":"86eef595a947d9707eb26dcda94e98456d065650","tid":1631482,"uid":66577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:52:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c5a41396989aa52ae4f0d903fbaf241d426d5de","tid":1631482,"uid":75543,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:52:36.000Z","msg":"呢到呢幾日係勁多五毛搞分化 建議手足暫時唔好上連登住 冷靜下先講真 去twitter做文宣好過喺呢到睇post留言<br />\n<br />\n利申: 勇武和理非永不割蓆 齊上齊落"},{"pid":"4a0bd91e9aa5ebae60cbd23005eac4b6813f43f4","tid":1631482,"uid":97603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:54:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4887a67fd814eb97cdc1914754cb301548b86a0","tid":1631482,"uid":66577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c5a41396989aa52ae4f0d903fbaf241d426d5de","tid":1631482,"uid":75543,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:52:36.000Z","msg":"呢到呢幾日係勁多五毛搞分化 建議手足暫時唔好上連登住 冷靜下先講真 去twitter做文宣好過喺呢到睇post留言<br />\n<br />\n利申: 勇武和理非永不割蓆 齊上齊落"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:54:25.000Z","msg":"我算好冷靜個批<br />\n但見到其他人失緊控 唉"},{"pid":"dbb11b138aebe5407f683eb8cde6bde7c0a451b4","tid":1631482,"uid":66577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:54:35.000Z","msg":"推多次"},{"pid":"d1fa7e0f47834ad0766a2631c4bc63f98e01a9f6","tid":1631482,"uid":66577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:55:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3607381fdf35d97256872562b186932adf809779","tid":1631482,"uid":66577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:58:44.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"487e311207a2c9a913f1f4537717dab8c6b7a023","tid":1631482,"uid":66577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:01:26.000Z","msg":"推多次"},{"pid":"3fbef1554f348fb821c24eb48931bb20603847dc","tid":1631482,"uid":66577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:01:50.000Z","msg":"我大大話話去左咁多場<br />\n聽下喇唔該"},{"pid":"896d29ee47e26b7850790067c60e3de15b5ac427","tid":1631482,"uid":49628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:02:17.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n真係要進化 次次出親都見好多人齋企 其實帶對手套已經幫到手"},{"pid":"d97b0d54d595de85d98f913dbfa11113546ecc0c","tid":1631482,"uid":89105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:07:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b11c307a5fb930dbcee17e28755a97f0a887992","tid":1631482,"uid":89105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:07:17.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"2ca076321d4920321d2f04ff54ae2b6399d58961","tid":1631482,"uid":225102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:07:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5b430f6ed10b12e6b2de78ff7231f368bf6b922","tid":1631482,"uid":66577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:09:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d012bb9afc7c1651b00ef66028d787b4c67a1e64","tid":1631482,"uid":66577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:16:09.000Z","msg":"推.."},{"pid":"f23a1b1b172c22428f807e13864c5d5e057a7636","tid":1631482,"uid":66577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:41:21.000Z","msg":"算喇 由佢 你地自己搞"},{"pid":"64f269354f78c4b0d645e4d56d917cfc8e34cc90","tid":1631482,"uid":66577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:29:05.000Z","msg":"推多嘢"},{"pid":"3f4579fc928753027b194e34bf6b5c3cf08d0332","tid":1631482,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:29:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"1165e106bd8e0d32834167078a02551cc4cbe754","tid":1631482,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:31:05.000Z","msg":"「認真」各位手足 借東風啊！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629930</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n新職業 忍者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻煩幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7136f9036e6403fc3193aab036370592218e9145","tid":1631482,"uid":205967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:35:27.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[沙田柚入]求下大家唔好再散去市中心！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631420</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3ec6e1fd0da9951391c43eb0a5209396e99ee152","tid":1631482,"uid":66577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:06:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09b9d510ab1adef870bc5e63a46821fba6e12901","tid":1631482,"uid":66577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:28:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"822791b6b9e9446d3922d3bb3f61ee4d55e488f6","tid":1631482,"uid":66577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:31:10.000Z","msg":"推多次"},{"pid":"86e6abde6601dcd98e51e125cfb775241d7b044b","tid":1631482,"uid":66577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:02:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b977577bee347013e543ed8f5ff6e7b1f3758a90","tid":1631482,"uid":65559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:03:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c74359e67a2a7d5e2b9f93d8266e712265ef3121","tid":1631482,"uid":329950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:05:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e593085b24645c17a4f7bda578b26e971d8a5580","tid":1631482,"uid":276948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:07:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fdecf49898cf31df6a6b035fba8162e7f891a380","tid":1631482,"uid":66577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply